azure<br />\nalicloud<br />\n都係呢d架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae76d3cb379f498115b00da4b8b69a89b47840c","tid":787953,"uid":116953,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"15e76dfbba5783160e6a89c6278e8f7a1f99bdb3","tid":787953,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n依家做緊既公司想轉web hosting<br />\n用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老細嫌佢服務唔好 想轉<br />\n<br />\n要求新既web hosting<br />\n要有100GB web Storage<br />\n支那國內直連到去公司個網<br />\n<br />\n無論香港定外國既web hosting都可以<br />\n<br />\n求推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"叫得 web hosting 多數都唔好架啦<br />\n因為做得好既都變哂 cloud<br />\n<br />\nbtw 你話老闆嫌人服務唔好先係重點<br />\n因為多數世界知名既 cloud server 都係自動化<br />\n上網比錢就即刻用得<br />\n唔知你老闆仲想要咩&quot;服務&quot;<br />\n<br />\n最多人用既 Cloud 一定係 AWS<br />\n好似 AWS, Azure, Google Computer Engine<br />\n性能好速度快<br />\n所有野可以自己微調<br />\n容量要幾多 TB 都得<br />\n唔起 server 都得 ( serverless）<br />\n容量/流量用幾多先收幾多<br />\n有得一年/限額免費試用<br />\n試下先都得<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有平價 Cloud<br />\nVultr, Digital Ocean, Linode<br />\n三間價錢都超平<br />\nDO 同 Linode 最平 USD$5 一個月<br />\nVultr 最平 USD$2.5 一個月<br />\n呢個價錢唔係 web hosting 喎！係 VPS <br />\n你可以當係成部 server 任你武<br />\n一部 VPS 可以放好多個 web<br />\n裝乜野版本既 Linux 都得<br />\n<br />\n至於大陸睇唔睇到<br />\n可能得 Google 係睇唔到<br />\n選 Server 時選香港/日本/新加坡通常都得 (但有時又會比大陸block)<br />\n<br />\n其他係 godaddy/namecheap 果D hosting 就唔推薦<br />\n因為廢"},{"pid":"118aa7321a9a2f2aeac261802cec71221d6a9dad","tid":787953,"uid":188714,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:36:07.000Z","msg":"點睇layerstack? 睇落香港公司，但行家話成日死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e48f7eb1da1f7fcfce783d44c58a52cd69e10ae","tid":787953,"uid":93646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eed